tingling of her aborted orgasm, almost tipping over the edge into ecstasy, but falling just short as Himari suddenly left her (much like their marriage).&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Alex ground pathetically on her ex-wife’s hip as they got into the elevator together. She pressed messy, open-mouthed kisses to Himari’s neck as she clung desperately to Himari’s still wet jacket. Alex's grip revealed that the black lace of Himari's undershirt, in fact, didn't hide her breasts at all. Her dusky nipples almost artistically displayed by the swirling pattern of the lace. Alex could feel her already crumbling self-control slipping through her fingers entirely. Could feel the desperate, sick obsession filling her up like sweet mercury.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;As they stumbled into Alex’s penthouse (Himari might have taken half her shit in the divorce, but half of an absurd generational fortune is still a fuck load of money.) Himari grabbed Alex by the hair, pulling back to meet her eyes.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;“There you are, Darling. Finally given in. Fuck, it always gets me so hard seeing you let go and be the pathetic, needy mess I married,” Himari said, her fist tightening in Alex’s hair until it hurt. She slid her other hand up Alex’s body and started to grope her tits through her dress.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;“That’s right, there’s the Alex I remember. This whole ‘Dr. Alexandra’ nonsense really doesn’t suit you,” Himari continued, and Alex could only moan. The feeling of the woman she loved touching her, using her body, filled her up with a twisted ecstasy that makes it hard for her to even think. The constant refrain of maybe this time she'd stay slipped loose from her control.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;“Now, show me what a good, obedient girl you are. Strip for me, and then get on your knees.”.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description>
