      <title>Girlfriend #32: Suru Kaeru-chan</title>
      <author> Thought_Prism </author>
      <link>https://www.scribblehub.com/series/1332557/girlfriend--suru-kaeruchan/</link>
      <comments>https://www.scribblehub.com/read/1332557-girlfriend--suru-kaeruchan/chapter/1338932/#comments</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">f88c89706d470c8a5df33551e976f537a0580cc4</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;div class="wi_fic_desc" property="description"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Aijou Rentarou, whose heart overflows with love, was accidentally blessed with 100 soulmates. Today, he meets his thirty-second girlfriend, who is as unique as all the rest. If anything, the fact that Kaeru is just MtF is more realistic than the quirks half his other future wives have. Ridiculously cute and stupid shenanigans abound within.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This is a fanfic of the ongoing 100Kanojo manga. If you haven’t read it up to the current chapter as of this story’s release, chapter 198, you’ll probably want to reference the wiki as you're reading given the sheer number of characters involved.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.scribblehub.com/read/1332557-girlfriend--suru-kaeruchan/chapter/1338932/"&gt;&lt;div class="chapter-title"&gt;Girlfriend #32: Suru Kaeru-chan&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div class="chp_raw" id="chp_raw"&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Today has been another very busy yet deeply fulfilling and lovey-dovey day for Aijou Rentarou so far. With his limitless capacity for affection, forged in steel from years of heartbreak, he works tirelessly to make sure every last woman in his life is as happy as they possibly can be. To Rentarou, no price is too high to pay for each of his many precious girlfriends, be it time, health, or the structural integrity of the fourth wall.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Oh, this is different. I must have stepped into in a fanfic AU at some point after that last crosswalk,” he idly noted aloud. Then, he stopped to make eye contact with the narrator, his expression deathly serious. “You’d better not write anything Nakamura-sensei wouldn’t.” &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;It will all be fine in the end like always.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Okay that’s good,” he said, perking back up before resuming his stroll. “I’ll just roll with it, then.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;At the moment, Rentarou was paying a rare visit to the Ohananomitsu university campus of his school complex to meet one of his girlfriends, Eira, for a date. He’d never been to the university’s student center, and Eira wanted to show him around, just walk for a while. Because he absolutely didn’t want to risk being late, Rentarou was arriving an hour early, and was planning to get his homework done in the meantime.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Around him, the campus was abuzz with students. It was a balmy spring day, and plenty of folks were taking advantage of the weather to toss frisbees around, lounge on the grass, or otherwise hang out. Rentarou smiled as he people-watched, his mind filling with many new ideas for ways to spend time with the loves of his life as he did.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;So entranced was he by thoughts of his girlfriends that, upon reaching the door of the student center, he did not notice another student also reaching for the handle at the same time. Their fingers brushed against eachother, his own large, gentle digits wrapped overtop against another set with pink polished nails.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Oh, I’m sorry!” a soft voice exclaimed, the second hand rapidly pulling back.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Rentarou turned to face its source, and his breath caught in his throat.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;For standing next to him was an incredibly cute woman. They were about the same height, so he could look right into her clear, blue eyes. Her long, blue hair cascaded down to her hips, the ends curled. She wore a frilly white sundress with knee-high socks, and her pink messenger bag matched the large ribbon tied behind her head. Onto the bag were pinned various buttons featuring video game characters.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Her lips were open slightly, apologetic, though that quickly changed to a look of awe and sudden longing as an electric ‘zing’ shot through her whole body, a sensation unlike anything she’d experienced before. Rentarou, however, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;had&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt; experienced it before. This was what it felt like to encounter your soulmate for the first time. An angelic choir sung in the background as the pair traded stares.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Rentarou recovered first, grabbing the door and pulling it open for her without breaking eye contact. “You’re fine, it was my fault for not paying attention to what I was doing!” he insisted. “After you.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“T-Thanks,” the woman replied, her shoes squeaking on the tile as she stepped past him and went inside. However, she had completely forgotten what it was she was here for, and instead waited right inside the atrium for Rentarou to follow, clutching the strap of her bag.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;He did, the door gently swinging closed behind him. Standing at a respectful distance, Rentarou smiled, all thoughts of schoolwork forgotten. He then immediately began to make conversation. “No problem. It’s the least I can do, especially since I’m just visiting from the high school and you actually attend here, I’m guessing. What’s your name?” he asked.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“I’m Kaeru. Suru Kaeru,” she answered automatically, unable to look away from Rentarou. “And yeah, I’m a freshman here at Ohananomitsu University.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“It’s really nice to meet you, Kaeru-chan,” Rentarou said. Then, he pointed to her bag. “Do you play games often?”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Oh, uh, yes,” she replied, using her free hand to brush a strand of hair off of her face. “I like pretty much every genre, though I avoid most multiplayer titles since the communities tend to be toxic.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“I can understand that!” went Rentarou, laughing. “I mostly play arcade games, and sometimes creeps will show up.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Kaeru nodded twice. “Don’t I know it.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;There was a brief pause before Rentarou continued, briefly lost in Kaeru’s eyes. “Well, I’ve got somewhere to be, soon, and I don’t want to keep you if you’re busy, but would you mind exchanging contact info?” he asked. “It’s not every day a guy runs into someone so cute for the first time!”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;At his words, Kaeru broke out into a furious blush, blinking a few times. She stood there next to him, working her jaw. “Y-You mean that? You really think I’m cute? Not…” she added under her breath, trailing off. Her head drooped.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Of course you’re cute!” Rentarou insisted, raising his fists in front of his chest to better convey his belief. “I’m practically a doctor of cuteness studies at this point, so when I say that you’re the most adorable woman in the whole world, you’d better believe it! I would date you in a heartbeat!”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Kaeru lifted her head back up. Studied Rentarou’s face. There was no trace of sleaze or dishonesty there, only the utmost conviction of a man who treated all women like queens.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Suddenly, she burst into tears, nearly tripping over her own feet as she dashed for a nearby unoccupied lounge chair, collapsing into it and burying her face in her hands.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Gasping, Rentarou hurried after her as quickly as possible, to the point of even kickflipping off the wall to vault over a large group of athletes all entering the building at once, many of whom clapped politely or whistled appreciatively at his parkour skills.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;When he reached Kaeru, sitting down in the adjacent chair, Rentarou’s concern spilled out of him in a torrent. “What’s wrong, Kaeru-chan? Are you okay? Was it something I said? Do you need some water? Or a handkerchief?” he asked, pulling both items out of his uniform jacket and offering them to her.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Eventually, her hands fell away from her face. “I-I wasn’t in any way prepared for this today,” Kaeru forced out between sobs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;As Rentarou gently brushed the corner of the handkerchief over the tear-streaks on her face, Kaeru’s cries gave way to stilted laughter. “Y-You’re fine, Rentarou-kun. These are tears of &lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;joy&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;. I just never imagined that I’d be able to fall in love at first sight, and that they would reciprocate without being repulsed because…”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Rentarou’s frown morphed into a confused line. “Why would you think that?” he pressed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Isn’t it obvious?” Kaeru began, leaning back in the chair. “Because I’m trans.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;She gestured to herself. And Rentarou gave her a once-over. Sighing, he placed his hand over hers again, this time on the armrest, squeezing softly.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Well, that certainly doesn’t matter to me,” Rentarou confirmed. “Sure, your shoulders might be a bit wide, and your feet might be a bit large. But every person’s body is already different, Kaeru-chan. You could have skin covered in burn scars, or pus-filled lesions, and I’d still reach out my hand to hold yours.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Kaeru turned to Rentarou. Her eyes glittered with unrestrained happiness, and a beaming grin grew from ear to ear.   &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“All I see is someone I want to go out with,” he continued, his own chest light with more butterflies than Yamame’s hair. “Will you be my girlfriend, Kaeru-chan?”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;In reply, she leaned over and kissed him, the whole world fading away into the background as their blooming love cascaded between their lips.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align:center"&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;*  *  *&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“... And so, due to how things panned out… Would you guys mind accepting Suru Kaeru-chan as my newest girlfriend…?!” Rentarou asked, sweat pouring down his face. Beside him stood Kaeru herself, who was still completely agog at the sheer scale of the Rentarou Family Polycule assembled on the high school rooftop as always.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“I do not understand why you keep asking,” stated Nano, adjusting her glasses with a finger. “We have already made clear we are fine with you even dating your own cousin; at this point any variant of girlfriend is logically going to be acceptable.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Here, little Chiyo fidgeted in embarrassment. “I still think dating Kusuri-san and Yaku-san at the same time is weirder, but yes, I agree, it’s okay.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Welcome to the family, Kaeru-chan!” Momoha exclaimed, raising a wine bottle high. “Cheers!”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;As the world’s least qualified ethics teacher resumed her day drinking, the others all began to crowd around Kaeru and Rentarou. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“A trans girl? How abnormal!” exclaimed Himeka before adopting a ponderous expression. “Maybe I should transition, too…”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Hakari elbowed her in the side. “That’s rude! Transitioning isn’t something anyone can just &lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;do&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;, only people with gender dysphoria transition. For example, I would never, as I am very happy with my body.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;For emphasis, Hakari struck a lewd pose, with her hand on her thigh and her boobs thrust forwards. She began chuckling to herself, watching Rentarou to see how happy &lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;he&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt; was. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;But alas, he was still focused on the others.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Tama can empathize. Tama also transitioned into a cat recently, meow,” said Tama, idly rolling around a yarn ball. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“This vast world of ours is full of all kinds, indeed,” Uto intoned as she posed sagely with her hand on her chin.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“It’s also very cruel,” added Meru. “For the world to allow one to be born in a body of the wrong gender; that is truly the pinnacle of despair.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Do not worry, though, dear Kaeru-chan, it is plain to see that you have done much to cultivate your feminine beauty,” said Mimimi, satisfied with her appraisal of Kaeru.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Yeah, like, your outfit is totes cute, for real,” confirmed Ahko with her typical lazy grin. “You gotta tell me where you got that ribbon later.”    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Overwhelmed by the show of support from her fellow girlfriends, Kaeru’s heart melted. “Thanks, everyone, really. I wish I could say more, but all this positive affirmation is too much! I can’t find the words!”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;From behind her Rentarou was bawling like an idiot, impossible amounts of elated tears falling from his eyes like waterfalls as he looked on with heart-shaped pupils. With practiced, professional motions, Mei began mopping up the rapidly flooding rooftop, her own eyes still shut as usual.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Meanwhile, Shizuka replied to Kaeru using her text-to-speech app. &amp;lt;I have trouble with that, too.&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“And if you ever run into a bigoted asshole on campus, just ring me up and I’ll come running to kick their skull in,” offered Eira. “I live in the dorms, so I can be there in a flash.” &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Kaeru snorted. “I won’t say no, but that might be overdoing it, I think.” &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Given all the crazy stuff that happens in this town, it probably isn’t,” said Kurumi, straight-manning. In the comedic sense, not the identity sense.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;However, Momiji was being the opposite of straight, and had snuck up behind Kaeru to reach around and grope her chest, as she was wont to do. Upon feeling the younger girl’s well-trained hands cupping her, Kaeru froze up and squeaked in surprise.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Yeah, Momiji-chan does that. You never really get used to it,” Meme explained, deflating slightly behind her bangs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Hmm…” Momiji uttered, savoring the sensation. “There’s more here than I was expecting. Nice. Karane-san is flatter.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Uh, well, the HRT helps,” said Kaeru, unsure whether to shove her away or not. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;In the background, multiple veins popped on Karane’s forehead, and she began to mutter a string of jealous obscenities. Rentarou, his tears now having ceased, moved over to hug her.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Um, I’m still confused, yes yes,” noted a visibly perplexed Yaku. “What exactly is this ‘trans-gender’ thing? Is it like those Kabuki actors who dress up as ladies?”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Not at all!” clarified Miss Naddy helpfully. “Transgender folks are becoming more widely accepted in ‘Murica these days. What it means is that Kaeru here wasn’t actually born as a girl, but realized she was one later. To be able to embrace your real gender identity is true freedom!”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Yaku tilted her head the other way, clearly still not getting it. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“You don’t need to understand, Grand Dame Yaku,” Saki reassured her. “It doesn’t matter what’s in her pants. Seniority is still what counts. And I respect you, Kaeru-senpai.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;At this, Kaeru’s smile faded. She hummed, turning to Saki. “I mean, I’m grateful, but it matters to &lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;me&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;. HRT is great and all, but I still wish my body was like, well, any of yours,” Kaeru said, making a sweeping gesture indicating everyone else.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“You do? Kusuri can help with that, yep yep,” interjected Kusuri, currently in her eight-year-old form. Biting her lip, she fished around in her lab coat and extracted a corked test tube with a bubbling orange liquid inside. “This is Kurusi’s new ‘Instant Bottom Surgery' drug, yep yep. It’s still got a few unpredictable side effects like—”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“HOLY SHIT GIMME,” went Kaeru, who swiped the test tube and chugged its contents so quickly that nobody could have possibly moved in time to stop her.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Nano stared. “Prior experience indicates something highly unusual will occur shortly.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Most everyone held their breath, watching Kaeru toss the empty test tube aside, covering her mouth with a hand as she let out a small, ladylike belch. The only sound on the rooftop came from Nemu’s light snores as she continued sleeping on her feet. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;The silence was broken when something fell onto the ground from beneath Kaeru’s skirts, landing with a soft ‘plop’ between her feet. Her eyes widened, shining. “It… actually worked. It worked!”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Rentarou squee’d in joy, basking in her happiness as both of them grinned from ear to ear. He rushed over to Kaeru, and the two of them embraced.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Congratulations, Kaeru-chan!” said Matsuri, jumping up and down. “We should start a festival to celebrate, eh?”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Mai, meanwhile, narrowed her eyes, glancing between Nano and the fallen ‘something’. “Maybe later. Right now, I’m still getting a bad feeling. Like a big mess my dear sister will need help cleaning up is about to happen.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Some of the other girls followed Mai’s gaze, noticing the object on the ground for the first time. It was, in fact, Kaeru’s penis, with the sack still attached. Chiyo and Shizuka blushed furiously, covering their faces. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“&lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Oh my&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;~” went Hahari.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“It’s a ‘6’!” Suu happily pointed out.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;And then it moved.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Karane flinched, jumping back. “Crap, what the hell?”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Slowly, it picked itself up, tiny legs growing out of the spot where it had been attached to Kaeru moments ago. Stretching to its full length, the opening on the strange creature’s head widened into a gaping maw, drool dripping from it. Above said mouth, two eyes opened, their slitted, reptilian pupils radiating malice. One clawed foot at a time, it stood.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Yamame shivered in fear. “I’ve seen some crazy dicks on ducks and such, but &lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;that isn’t natural&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“It’s cool though,” slurred Momoha. “Just think about all the fun stuff you could do with—”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Mai cut her off, covering her mouth and pulling Momoha back. Most of the others were watching the suddenly-independent trouser snake warily, backing away, though Kaeru and Rentarou were still celebrating. Iku jabbed Rentarou in the side to get his attention, then physically turned both him and Kaeru towards it, concerned.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“W-What in Buddha’s name…?” Kaeru uttered.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Trusting her instincts, Kishika drew her wooden sword and dropped into a battle stance. “State your intentions, strange beast. If they are pure, you will be spared.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;The penis entity did not speak. Instead, it hissed, then lunged. Mouth stretching further to an impossible width, it charged at Suu, who was closest. Then, it began to &lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;inhale&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;, a vortex of air swirling inwards like how it worked with Kirby. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Half the girls started screaming, including Suu herself, as Suu was sucked in by the force and immediately swallowed whole. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“SUU-CHAN!” Rentarou cried, his countenance contorting in rage. “HOW DARE YOU!”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;As Rentarou pulled out a pair of brass knuckles and put them on, huffing steam like a bull, the beast rapidly swelled larger, from its original, modest size to that of a person. However, before Rentarou could beat the meat into submission, Kishika struck, being faster. With a mighty swing of her blade and a shout, she knocked it away with great force, sending the penis monster tumbling overhead all the way to the other side of the building, where it landed with a crash.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;However, it was merely bruised, not defeated, and the nefarious nethers stood, screeching as its claws scraped the roof.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Rentarou Family scrambled, many of the girls clumping together in panic. Meme vanished completely, leaving a plushie in her place in a feat of misdirection. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;The rest readied themselves to fight, forming a defensive perimeter. Alongside Rentarou and Kishika, Iku had her baseball bat at the ready, and Eira was crouched low in her well-trained capoeira stance. Yaku and Karane only had their bare fists, but for them, that was plenty.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Only Hakari and Hahari were degenerate enough to do neither, the two of them instead drooling at the sight of a penis the size of their whole body.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“What kind of impossible side effect is &lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;that&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;?!” Kaeru exclaimed, not yet used to the level of nonsense which befell the group on a daily basis. “It’s like a Shin Megami Tensei boss!”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Come at me, beast!” taunted Iku, raising her bat. “I can take whatever punishment you can dish out!”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;With an unholy roar, the creature charged, and the battle commenced. Eira whirled around and launched a furious back kick into the beast’s center of mass, but it raised a claw to block. Once more inhaling, Kishika had to abate her stabbing lunge and roll out of the way as it spun its head towards her.   &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“You can do it, guys! I believe in you!” encouraged Himeka with idol-like energy even as she had assumed the fetal position on the ground. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Miss Naddy patted her gently. “Wish I had one o’ those ‘Murican assault weapons right about now.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“So do I,” quipped Mei. “Alas, some things are beyond even Mistress Hahari’s purchasing power.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Focus on protecting them, yes yes,” said Yaku, who was drawing the voracious rod’s attention, nimbly avoiding being swallowed with both hands behind her back.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Case in point, Nemu was striding purposefully towards the melee, her dreaming personality evidently wanting to help while simultaneously massively overestimating her own ability. Saki was trying to hold her back, but she was too small, and Nemu was slowly dragging her along, Saki’s shoes scraping the ground. “Stop, Nemu-kouhai! Just because you’re dreaming doesn’t mean you’re invincible!”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;With a gasp, Iku interposed herself between the mutant penis and the two of them, striking it with her bat so hard a crack rent the air. "Ha!"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;However, it was not enough. Rearing back, the monster sucked more strongly than it had ever sucked before. Iku moaned as she was yanked off her feet, through the air, and swallowed. Saki screamed as she and Nemu were also lifted upwards.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“NOOOO!” Rentarou wailed, leaping after them. He reached his girlfriends just as they were halfway down the monster’s gullet, grabbing each of them with a hand. He planted his feet against its head, pulling with all the unleashed strength of a protective boyfriend to keep them from being swallowed. But Rentarou and the giant penis were equally matched, and they were locked in a stalemate. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Unable to avert her eyes from the spectacle, Rin trembled from behind Yamame. “This sort of violence isn’t &lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;molto violento. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;I don’t want to be eaten!” &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Not even a synchronized pummeling from Karane, Eira, and Kishika could get the beast to loosen its grip. Instead, it overwhelmed Rentarou by doubling in size, having incorporated Iku into itself, and then fully ate Nemu and Saki.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Despite this, Rentarou valiantly refused to let go, and was pulled inside along with them!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“&lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Rentarou&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;!” his assembled girlfriends all cried out in unison, their voices cracking.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Surprisingly, though, Rentarou was immediately spat back out.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Relief and confusion swept through them in unison. “He’s okay,” said Usa-chan, breathless.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“I suppose it does not see the beauty in men and refuses to eat them,” added Mimimi. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Such might be the way of the penis. Or it might not be,” Uto concurred in her typical noncommittal fashion.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;As Rentarou rose, eyes alight with flames and the fury of a guardian in his bones, the dastardly dick once again doubled in size, now twelve feet tall and still kicking despite its wounds. It once more screeched in challenge. Mei dashed in, taking up Iku’s fallen baseball bat in her own hands to reinforce the line, and the battle resumed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Why is this even happening, anyway?” wondered Ahko aloud as she shook in fright. “Wasn’t that drug only supposed to, like, change Kaeru-chan’s stuff, or whatever?”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“If I had to guess, it is poetic, like a fairy tale,” Meru theorized. “Kaeru-chan has forever seen her penis as monstrous, and thus, when it separated from her, that is what it became: a monster.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Is that true, Kaeru-chan?” Rentarou asked, concerned. He stopped pummeling the monster’s nuts like a speedbag to make eye-contact with her over his shoulder. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Yes, it is,” Kaeru admitted, dejected and ashamed. She clung onto a nonplussed Tama for support.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Well, don’t worry, this isn’t your fault!” Rentarou reassured her, even as he continued his deadly dance with the hungry snake.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“But it’s true that none of this would have happened if I wasn’t here,” Kaeru insisted with a sob, turning away from Tama and crumpling in on herself. “I’ve already hurt you so much. If only I’d just stayed in my room and played Fire Emblem all day, then we wouldn’t have even met. And everyone would still be okay.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Don’t beat yourself up, Kaeru-chan! Love is always worth fighting for!” Rentarou countered, pushing back his own pain over those who'd been swallowed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Hakari nodded firmly, kneeling down next to Kaeru. “This isn’t the first time he nearly lost one of us forever, and it won’t be the last. Whatever happens, Rentarou-san never gives up.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“We need ideas. Is there anything we can do to stop this thing and get it to spit everyone out?” Rentarou asked.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;At this, Kurumi grabbed Kusuri by her shoulders. “Oh yeah, don’t you have that Negation Drug or whatever? Maybe if Kaeru-chan takes it this monster will go away!”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Kusuri does have some today, yep yep,” Kusuri confirmed. “However…” She slowly turned to Kaeru.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Kaeru looked between the ongoing skirmish against her former member and the pair of Kusuri and Kurumi with an expression of profound conflict. “I… you guys all seem great, really, and I definitely don’t want anyone to die because of me, but… having a body without &lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;that&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt; has been my dream for so long. There has to be another way!” she pleaded.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Like &lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;what&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;?” pressed Karane, getting the monster’s shaft in a brutal chokehold as it thrashed about.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Hit with a spark of inspiration, Momiji boldly stepped forwards. “I’m gonna try groping it. Penises like that, right?”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;She only got like three steps before the beast threw Karane off and inhaled her, growing even larger.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“No!” cried Usa-chan. “Everyone’s getting eaten! At this rate, I’m gonna be all alone out here!” Sniffling, she too ran out of the group, leaping directly towards the penis’ head, arms outstretched. “Take me, too!”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;It did. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Matsuri facepalmed. &amp;lt;That darn fool,&amp;gt; said Shizuka.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“I would have advised running the other way,” noted Mei, continuing to strike at the penis’s claws with her borrowed bat. “But if we all fled, this monster would only begin to devour the innocent.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“And nobody at this school deserves to be eaten. All of you have long lives ahead, yes yes,” went Yaku, backflipping to avoid a raging thrust, the penis’ hateful eyes following her movement.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Right. While being vored is certainly an abnormal way to go, I would disappoint my fans if I left them all so soon,” said Himeka before shooting Kaeru a pleading look directly, since both were still on the ground. “You’re the star of this show, Kaeru-chan, and you’re the one who needs to end this.” &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Yes, please make a decision, Kaeru-chan!” Eira exclaimed, kicking the monster in the balls. “Even I can’t keep this up forever!”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“I probably could with these,” joked Hahari, who was cupping her own breasts through her suit jacket.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“This is serious, Hahari-san!” scolded Chiyo. “It’s a life-changing choice for Kaeru-senpai to make!”  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;At this, Kaeru averted her gaze in thought, her shoulders still slumped. “I… I don’t…”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“We won’t force you one way or the other,” Rentarou reassured her gently, even as his whole body was tensed for battle. “But I would appreciate it if you made a decision soon. If I used my full power, I could throw this dick into the void between the pages, never to hurt you again, but then I’d also have to go back in time to get the others back, which opens a huge can of narrative worms to deal with.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Meru nodded, shutting her dark eyes. “Even I would not attempt to pen a tale including time travel due to the confusion that would induce in readers.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“People are already starting to get overwhelmed just by the sheer number of us,” added Kurumi between bites of a double cheeseburger she’d procured from somewhere for stress-eating.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Nobody spoke for a long moment, the only sounds being those of the mighty struggle between girlfriend and girlcock raging in the background. The display of fighting prowess from both sides brought to mind some of the greatest battles in anime and manga history, but this narrator will spare the details since this is not a serious adventure story.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Rather, the important part here is Kaeru’s emotional state. Pursing her lips, a whole range of emotions passed her face as she looked between Rentarou and the other girls. Envy towards hourglass figures, pain at watching them suffer, regret for opportunity lost. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;But she also saw the rest of Rentarou’s Family still present studying her with their various levels of care and personal expressiveness. There was no anger, no blame, only acceptance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Kaeru’s own eyes softened, and her heart was set. She straightened and rose, standing tall, and took a deep breath. “I’ll do it. I’ll take the Negation Drug.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Thank goodness,” sighed Yamame. The squirrel on her head seemed equally relieved. “I was afraid this would turn into another apocalyptic event.” &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Really? What *&lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;urp&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;* made you change your mind?” Momoha asked Kaeru before the latter could process what exactly Yamame just said.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Well, it’s just… I remembered how kindly all of you treated me, how you &lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;still&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt; are, and how much love Rentarou-san showered me with. It was far more than I’d ever felt before, even prior to taking Kusuri-chan’s drug,” Kaeru explained, smiling slightly as she gazed towards Rentarou.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Rentarou, for his part, melted, his liquid-like body allowing him to dodge a viscous sweep from the snarling abomination.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Rentarou-san indeed has that effect on people, and brings it out in us,” said Nano, who was smiling on the inside. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Miss Naddy placed a hand on her hip. “Shoot, o’ course we’d give you a warm welcome!” &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Hmph,” Mai harrumphed, in peak &lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;tsun&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt; mode. “Nobody can hope to compare to my dear older sister, but I do admire your resilience.” &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Thanks,” Kaeru said, briefly overcome. “I realize now that it doesn’t actually matter what’s between my legs. I was already valid to everyone who matters,” she declared, shining brightly. “If you can accept me as I am, with the equipment I was born having, then I can, too.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Aww,” cooed Ahko and Rentarou at the same time, the latter also making his trademark open-mouthed ‘enraptured with love’ face. “Don’t say that. I, like, can’t take it,” added Ahko.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Well said, my friend,” echoed Mimimi, striking a satisfied pose.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Great, you’re self-affirmed. Now take the freaking Negation Drug already!” Karane ordered, heaving with exertion as she continued to wrestle with the giant penis beast, barely keeping it under control.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Ah, right,” said Kaeru, blanching a bit as she turned to Kusuri. Without needing to be told, Kusuri pulled out another tube, this one containing a less ominous liquid. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Kaeru grabbed and uncorked it, but did not tip it back immediately. For a long moment, she stared, using her other hand to poke between her legs. “Goodbye, sweet vagina. I hardly knew ye.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Pushing back her longing, she took the drug.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;The effect was immediate. Opposite Kaeru and the other noncombatants, her penis let out a wail of pain as its unholy frame convulsed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Yeah, eat shit and die, you fiend!” cried Rin, reveling in its suffering.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Rentarou, Karane, Mei, Kishika, and Yaku all disengaged from the monster, retreating to a safe distance as it flailed about, collapsing onto its side. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Everyone watched with bated breath as Kaeru’s penis wretched a few times, its predatory eyes dilated in nausea, before barfing out Usa-chan, her body covered in sticky fluid.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;She sat up woozily, shaking her head. “Wow, that sure was something!”  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Rentarou cried in relief, rushing over to hug her and ignoring the resulting gross squelching noises as he peppered her cheek with kisses. Kaeru and the rest of the girls were equally elated to see her unharmed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Next came Momiji, then Saki, Nemu, Iku, and finally Suu, Rentarou repeating his prior ritual with each of them in turn. With every girl the thing squirted out, it shrunk down, until, with the loss of Suu, it returned to its original size.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Kaeru slowly stepped over to her penis as its monstrous features began to fade away, clawed legs retracting and snake eyes melding back into its head. She stared down at it, brows furrowed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Once it had returned to normal, some nebulous magical force sent it up through the air and under her dress, where it returned from whence it came - inside her panties - never to slurp up someone again. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“It’s over,” Kaeru exhaled, running her hands through her hair to spruce it back up.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;From where he currently knelt with Suu’s dizzy head on his lap, Rentarou beamed with renewed infatuation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Tama ran over to Kaeru’s side on all fours, nuzzling against her leg. “Tama is proud of you. You have a human’s courage, meow.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Twas the chivalrous path you took,” agreed Kishika, sheathing her sword.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Uto raised a hand dramatically. “I shall spread the tale of your triumph against your evil genitals far and wide across the land.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Kaeru’s eyes widened. “&lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Please&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt; don’t do that, Uto-chan.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;As half the group broke out into fits of giggling, Meme returned from wherever it was she’d been hiding. “I’m just glad everything is back to normal.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Guess that wasn’t a dream, huh?” said the now-awake but lethargic Nemu as she gave herself a once-over.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Eh, I’m gonna need a long bath, though,” said Saki as she shook slime off of her arms.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“We can go together,” said Suu in reply. Iku gave a thumbs-up.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Yay, a group activity! Let’s all go to the bathhouse!” cheered Usa-chan, pulling Mimimi and Yamame into an embrace. Yamame didn’t seem to mind, smiling, but Mimimi was aghast, screaming as the sticky goo from Usa-chan marred her clothes and hair.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Seeing his girlfriends happy as usual once more, Rentarou smiled wide. He approached Kaeru, who was also smiling at their antics. “All’s well that ends well. I’m positively elated to have you, Kaeru-chan.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Me too, Rentarou. I don’t regret any of this; running into you was still the best thing that ever happened to me. I love you,” she declared.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;As one, the two of them moved in for a soft kiss, love blossoming anew between them under the warm glow of the sun.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;When they separated, none of the others moved in for their own kisses. There would be plenty of time for shared affections later, and even the still-sloshed Momoha could recognize that this was their moment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;&amp;lt;A beautiful occasion,&amp;gt; smiled Shizuka.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“I really really really really really love you too, Kaeru-chan,” said Rentarou, lewdly taking her hand.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“And hey,” he continued, “if you do ever want to feel what it’s like to have a… you-know-what down there again, Kaeru-chan, we can always break out the Reborn as a New You drug from all the way back in Chapter 23.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Oh yes, I remember, that was quite fun,” noted Hahari with a wistful expression.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“You’d just need to find someone willing to swap bodies with you, yep yep,” Kusuri elaborated cheerfully.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Kaeru’s jaw dropped. “THAT’S A THING?!” &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style="text-align:center"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;i&gt;~ The End ~&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;div class="wi_authornotes"&gt; &lt;div&gt; &lt;div class="p-avatar-wrap"&gt;&lt;a class="avatar has-link" href="/profile/41958/thought_prism/"&gt;&lt;img id="acc_ava_change profile" alt="" src="https://cdn.scribblehub.com/avatar/s/10/ava_41958_1648260823.jpg"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="an_username"&gt;&lt;a href="/profile/41958/thought_prism/"&gt;Thought_Prism&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div style="clear: both;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="wi_authornotes_body"&gt;  Thanks for reading! As a bit of trivia, Kaeru’s design was mainly inspired by Rosado from Fire Emblem: Engage, who is the most blatantly trans-coded character I’ve ever seen. Even though the game’s writers left them as a femboy for some reason, the cowards. Anyway, that’s why Engage is Kaeru’s favorite game.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description>
