      <title>&amp;#8230;But My Mind Holds the Key</title>
      <author> DrMajalis </author>
      <link>https://www.scribblehub.com/series/1332653/but-my-mind-holds-the-key/</link>
      <comments>https://www.scribblehub.com/read/1332653-but-my-mind-holds-the-key/chapter/1332655/#comments</comments>
