      <description>&lt;div class="wi_fic_desc" property="description"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Far into our future, humanity has spread out amongst the stars to every corner of the galaxy. Samuel had always dreamed of being amongst the stars but never had the opportunity to escape life on New Eden. When tragedy strikes, Samuel wakes up in a new body on the Stellar Reach starship. How will the newly named Cassie adjust to this new life?&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This will most likely end up being a polyamorous MFF relationship, so if you don't like that and are looking for romance, I don't suggest reading it!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;TW: Religious abuse, strict gender roles, death, trauma, abuse&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;(This is my first time writing a full book and this is very much a rough draft so constructive feedback would be helpful!)&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description>
